name: Roboto Factory - Part Seven
description:
While prototype designer Xelda Jara has taken a creative hiatus and is looking for new directions. The DAO side and employees are concerned and expectant about the future of Roboto Factory Inc. 
Will they be out of a job? Will the team of scientists have to leave for other multinationals? Will the price of the cryptocurrency drop significantly? What will be the future of this industrial empire. Will art collectors start selling their shares? What will happen? Will it be the end or will this story continue?
